messages.message: Cleaned up the code style doc and added links within a few onboarding documents (and it can be found within the onboarding folder). Feel free to add to it over time, and also for new hires, link them to this doc on their first PR if they seem to have lots of style fixes needed: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1v4uw2Ziudu03dsARAULB2XeJcsL9bEA3ueGT1BzDgik
I'm planning on adding some javascript stuff today - feel free to change anything if it's not what people are used to doing!
